<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨吃惊地看着信使。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是什么问题？”观音菩萨问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是关于唐僧的。”信使说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为了成佛，他得经历九九八十一难。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我刚才看了一下他经历的劫难。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有80个。要想成佛，唐僧得再经历一难！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们走得真快啊！”唐僧笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人正向东飞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雷音寺的门将正念着咒语带他们飞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63294</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“西天取经要是这么简单就好了。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。“到达西天前，师父还是个凡人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那时候不能抬着师父走。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净看了看前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们马上就要到达大唐了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，一个信使追上了他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>信使在门将的耳边小声说了什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88607</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门将悄悄地看了一眼师徒四人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他回头看着信使，点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咒语马上就解除了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人从天上掉了下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！他们狠狠地摔在一条大河边的河岸上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空站起来，看见门将和信使在向西飞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么回事？”唐僧起身拍了拍袈裟上的土。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“门将为什么扔下了我们？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我告诉您为什么。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是个坏蛋，觉得把人扔下去有意思！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒朝那个门将晃了晃拳头，但他已经飞得很远了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“坏蛋！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空慢慢地转身看着唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我好像知道他为什么扔下我们了，师父。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>您为了成佛，得经历九九八十一难。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可能在全部都经历之前，您就到达了西天。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，天啊。”唐僧发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就是说，现在我还得再经历一次劫难，对吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空点了点头。“只希望问题不要太多。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第一个问题是要过这条河。”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“河很眼熟。”唐僧说，“在我们去西天的路上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们肯定过过这条河。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，河里浮上来一个巨大的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201551</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是只巨大的老龟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们好。”老龟说，“还记得我吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，记得。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“几年前，是你驮着我们过河的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”老龟说，“还有，我愿意再一次驮你们过河。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到我的壳上来吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人走了上去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老龟开始向河的对岸游去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净和八戒很快就睡着了，悟空在坐禅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧没有睡觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他坐在老龟脑袋附近</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们到达西天了吗？”老龟问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”唐僧说，“那是一个美丽的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们现在要返回东方，把真经交给大唐。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了。”老龟说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您问佛祖我什么时候才能修成人身了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧咬了咬嘴唇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他忘了问老龟的问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287933</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您不回答。”老龟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287933</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起。”唐僧说，“我，啊——”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哗啦！老龟突然沉入水中，把自己背上的人都扔到了水里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空一碰到凉水，眼睛一下子就睁开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跳到空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒、悟净和马迅速飞过了河。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，唐僧在急流中拼命挣扎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“帮帮我！”唐僧喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空念咒语把唐僧和行李从河里升了上来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都上岸后，悟空把行李倒了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水流了出来，卷轴也掉了出来，都湿透了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>348984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>355454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真经！”唐僧大喊，“真经都毁了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>